 1. You can change ads detecting threshold in settings 
 2. Some video downloaded corrupted in multi thread mode, use One thread for downloading in such situations 

 For Video Downloading: 
 
 1. Press button,in dialog select resolution, if available, and press colored button 
 
 2, 3. Press Play on video player on page with video, after that video should be detected. 
 
 If not try to press reload videos on video page or try reload page and repeat. 
 If not email me.

 For video detecting go to video in browser, click play and waite until video detected(can take 5–50 seconds) 
 1. You can change ads detecting threshold in settings 
 2. Video Detection not working for some web sites in mobile mode, try use desktop version of web site if video not detecting in mobile mode 
 If not try to press reload videos on video page or try reload page and repeat. 
 If not email me.
 

 For Video Downloading: 
 
 1. Press Download button,in appeared screen select resolution, if available 
 
 2. Press press download button.
